#: ../../../news.rst:166
msgid ""
"Raise a warning if a GSSAPI connection is obtained using the "
"``gssencmode=prefer`` libpq default (see :ticket:`#1136`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:171
msgid ""
"In a future Psycopg version the default in the binary package will be "
"changed to ``disable``. If you need to interact with the GSSAPI reliably you "
"should explicitly set the gssencmode_ parameter in the connection string or "
"the :envvar:`PGGSSENCMODE` environment variable to ``prefer`` or ``require``."
msgstr ""

